            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-66ea8929-26b8-4c94-a7d2-93b2adcb49eb">
                Mr. Boyd-Carpenter  (Kingston-upon-Thames)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-66ea8929-26b8-4c94-a7d2-93b2adcb49eb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
