<p class="">I did not say "Rubbish" at all. What I said was that it was optional for the person to be called up.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-49240d3d-e2d8-4542-83b0-a098e0438f10" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
