, G. S.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Parkin, B. T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stewart, Michael (Fulham, E.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wyatt, W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Paton, J. (Norwich)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stoddart-Scott, Col. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>York, C.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pearson, A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Strauss, H. G. (English Universities)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Young, Sir R. (Newton)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pearl, Capt. T. F.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stross, Dr. B.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Younger, Hon. Kenneth</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Peto, Brig. C. H. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stuart, Rt. Hon. J. (Moray)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td></td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pickthorn, K.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stubbs, A. E.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>TELLERS FOR THE AYES:</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Piratin, P.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Studholme, H. G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mr. Collindridge and Mr. Daines.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division"> </table></p><p class="Division"> <table type="span"></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td align="center" colspan="3"></p><p class="Division">  <b>NOES.</b></p><p class="Division"> </td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ayles, W. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hudson, J. H. (Ealing, W.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Richards, R.