            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b199d773-85d4-4cd2-bf0e-c3cdc19c6afb">
                Mr. S. Silverman
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b199d773-85d4-4cd2-bf0e-c3cdc19c6afb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
