                Mr. Hopkin Morris
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7bee11c2-a475-43f7-8361-edc0573d886a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-05-06/debates/bbb66728-34ae-4ca3-9fde-fb4aa0cb4fcc/Clause1%E2%80%94(LiabilityToBeCalledUpForService)#contribution-7bee11c2-a475-43f7-8361-edc0573d886a">
